            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Amazon Prime Day 将于 7 月 16 日开始，相信各位 unwire 读者最关注的当然是电子产品，小编特意在 Amazon 选了一些大家可能有兴趣的折扣产品，各位朋友可以看看有没有适合你的产品。</p><p>Amazon 现时已经开放香港满额免运费优惠。如果在购买页面见到「无进口手续费押金且免费送货至香港」，就代表这件商品支援免运费优惠；如果看见「无进口费用押金且 HKD XX 运费配送至香港」这句话，就代表 Amazon 官方会提供直送服务至香港，但买家需额外缴付运费。</p><p>另外要注意的是，Amazon Prime Day 大部分优惠需要先申请 Prime 会员才会有折扣。而且，Amazon 自家电子产品的优惠仅提供给北美用户，香港用户可能需要找美国朋友帮忙。</p><h2>SSD</h2><p>SanDisk 4TB Extreme PRO 便携式 SSD</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1178047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/81gHMgXQybL._AC_SY450_.jpg" alt="" width="486" height="450" /></p><p>SanDisk 4TB Extreme PRO 便携式 SSD 采用 USB 3.2 介面，读写速度高达 2000 MB/s，原价约为 HKD 2810，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="2328.5123125">2,328</span>。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08HN37XC1">购买连结</a></p><p>SAMSUNG 990 PRO SSD 4TB PCIe 4.0 M.2 2280 – M.2 SSD</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250382" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/81wug6lqudl_ac_sl150-694x193.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="193" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/81wug6lqudl_ac_sl150-694x193.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/81wug6lqudl_ac_sl150.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>SAMSUNG 990 PRO SSD 4TB PCIe 4.0 M.2 2280 – M.2 SSD 顺序读取/写入速度高达 7,450/6,900 MB/s，可达到接近 PCIe 4.0 的最大效能。原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="3630.1071815">3,630.11</span>，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="2341.9769315">2,341.98</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/SAMSUNG-Computing-Workstations-MZ-V9P4T0B-AM/dp/B0CHGT1KFJ/">购买连结</a></p><h2>智能手机</h2><p>Google Pixel 7 Pro 256GB</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250396" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61cbmzkbyl_ac_sl1500-465x580.jpg" alt="" width="465" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61cbmzkbyl_ac_sl1500-465x580.jpg 465w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61cbmzkbyl_ac_sl1500.jpg 722w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 465px" /></p><p>Google Pixel 7 Pro 使用 6.7 吋萤幕，并且拥有广角及超广角镜头，最高可达 30 倍 Super Res Zoom。原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="7799.44275">7,799.44</span> ，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="3458.61175">3,458.61</span>。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Google-Pixel-Pro-Smartphone-Telephoto/dp/B0BCQXG46W/ref=sr_1_2?crid=34X5IQOB61LLF&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.Ky5uZv0n60-tanNBXtCK21qgMWHAbch9tMDmg5iqF8G2TqBTtHpht1cW72-PGz3IyH6SMmRXrVeK2fuMYmIEUcF-vW7Bj7q7MjP3ZINU34-uY-oZq41XQ2E6SSztyiJF4YTG8-OTUSBVjxyg8pXczQ0wWA0Bm6ZZtka7i7P_aPSEHsYg7NfA49MfxQek8izS23gLcr6G1lQF4AavVs8j7pIVQJo99rkj1ZS7DBT6ilE.Bh0LHqCM96S8KaW_7efxq9Yr5LtqjyxtgUA2ds3t_p4&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=Google%2BPixel&amp;qid=1721028187&amp;sprefix=%2Caps%2C332&amp;sr=8-2&amp;th=1">购买连结</a></p><p>Google Pixel 8a 128GB</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250402" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71xoyjfgizl_ac_sl150-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71xoyjfgizl_ac_sl150-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71xoyjfgizl_ac_sl150.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71xoyjfgizl_ac_sl150-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>Google Pixel 8a 今年 5 月才刚刚推出，是次 Amazon Prime Day 也有优惠。Pixel 8a 是 Pixel 8 系列的中阶机型，使用 Google Tensor G3。原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="3895.8601649999996">3,895.86</span> ，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="3505.4934149999995">3,505.49</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Google-Pixel-8a-Unlocked-Advanced/dp/B0CYQFJSRF/">购买连结</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/30/amazon-prime-day-tiktok-shop-promotion/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Amazon Prime Day 下月中举行   TikTok 一周前办促销活动抢饮头啖汤</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>智能手表</h2><p>Apple Watch Ultra（第一代）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/810jr81lisl_ac_sl150-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/810jr81lisl_ac_sl150-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/810jr81lisl_ac_sl150.jpg 808w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><p>Apple Watch Ultra 具有防水功能，电池续航力达 36 小时，适合喜欢运动、探险的用家。原价约为 HKD 4,363.69，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="3895.32374">3,895.32</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-Ultra-Cellular-Titanium/dp/B0C7PJTHVM?ref=dlx_deals_dg_dcl_B0C7PJTHVM_dt_sl14_1f">购买连结</a></p><h2>无线耳机／喇叭</h2><p>Echo Dot (5th Gen) with Echo Buds (2023 Release)</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250442" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71ndb05ygel_ac_sl150-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71ndb05ygel_ac_sl150-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71ndb05ygel_ac_sl150.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71ndb05ygel_ac_sl150-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>这是一个套装组合，有 Echo Dot（第 5 代）及 Echo Buds（2023 年版本）。用家可以利用 Echo Buds 无缝连接至任何兼容 Alexa 的装置，继续播放。原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="780.4563775">780.46</span> ，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="390.15012749999994">390.15</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Echo-Deep-Blue-Release-Black/dp/B0C3DPZ9LQ?ref=dlx_deals_dg_dcl_B0C3DPZ9LQ_dt_sl14_1f">购买连结</a></p><p>JBL Tune Flex 无线蓝牙耳机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250413" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61joerbxerl_ac_sl150-627x580.jpg" alt="" width="627" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61joerbxerl_ac_sl150-627x580.jpg 627w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61joerbxerl_ac_sl150.jpg 973w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 627px" /></p><p>JBL Tune Flex 真无线蓝牙耳机电池续航力长达 32 小时，备有 IPX4 防水防汗功能，让用家可以在运动时享受音乐。原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="780.3046525">780.30</span> ，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="468.0266525">468.03</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/JBL-Tune-Flex-Wireless-Cancelling/dp/B0C1QNRGHC?ref=dlx_deals_dg_dcl_B0C1QNRGHC_dt_sl14_1f&amp;th=1">购买连结</a></p><h2>即影即有菲林</h2><p>Fujifilm Instax Mini Instant Film Value Pack &#8211; 120 Photos</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250480" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61gu1xu2wml_ac_sl115-667x580.jpg" alt="" width="667" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61gu1xu2wml_ac_sl115-667x580.jpg 667w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61gu1xu2wml_ac_sl115.jpg 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 667px" /></p><p>Fujifilm 即影即有菲林。原价约为 HKD 832.43，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="624.3419475">624.34</span> ，平均每张菲林大约 HKD 5.2。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Fujifilm-Instax-Mini-Instant-Value/dp/B07NWRG5T4">购买连结</a></p><h2>家庭电器</h2><p>Instant Pot Duo Plus 9 合 1 压力煲</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250407" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71czderg3l_ac_sl1500-554x580.jpg" alt="" width="554" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71czderg3l_ac_sl1500-554x580.jpg 554w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71czderg3l_ac_sl1500.jpg 859w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 554px" /></p><p>Instant Pot Duo Plus 是一款内置慢煮、煮饭、制作乳酪、保温等 9 项功能的压力煲，用家可以使用内置程式及手机应用程式控制这个压力煲，烹调各式各样的𩠌菜。原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="1014.7935829500001">1,014.79</span> ，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="585.11253975">585.11</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Instant-Pot-Plus-60-Programmable/dp/B01NBKTPTS?ref=dlx_deals_dg_dcl_B01NBKTPTS_dt_sl14_1f&amp;th=1">购买连结</a></p><p>De&#8217;Longhi Magnifica Evo 咖啡机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250410" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51dmbfo41sl_ac_sl108-446x580.jpg" alt="" width="446" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51dmbfo41sl_ac_sl108-446x580.jpg 446w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51dmbfo41sl_ac_sl108.jpg 692w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 446px" /></p><p>De&#8217;Longhi Magnifica Evo 内置 7 种一键即冲咖啡配方，同时设有 13 种研磨方式，原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="7025.405678">7,025.41</span> ，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="4293.151678">4,293.15</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/DeLonghi-ECAM29084SB-Magnifica-LatteCrema-Espresso/dp/B0B38KRTV6?ref=dlx_deals_dg_dcl_B0B38KRTV6_dt_sl14_1f">购买连结</a></p><p>Shark AI Ultra Voice Control Robot Vacuum AI 声控吸尘机械人</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61yq2hurpl_ac_sl1400-576x580.jpg" alt="" width="576" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61yq2hurpl_ac_sl1400-576x580.jpg 576w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61yq2hurpl_ac_sl1400.jpg 894w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61yq2hurpl_ac_sl1400-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 576px" /></p><p>Shark AI Ultra Voice Control Robot Vacuum 具有 Matrix Clean 功能，吸尘机械人可以侦测家中甚么地方有垃圾。另外有自动清空垃圾功能，底座可容纳 60 日份量的垃圾。用家可以使用 Amazon Alexa 或 Google Assistant 设定清洁计划，控制机械人在甚么时候吸尘。原价约为 HKD 4,675.46 ，现减至 HKD 2,302.40 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Shark-AV2511AE-Self-Empty-Capacity-Navigation/dp/B09T4YZGQR/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ref_=dlx_deals_sc_dcl_img_dt&amp;pd_rd_w=hDJw3&amp;content-id=amzn1.sym.cb099553-8b1e-4ecd-bf9d-2789a0a6379a&amp;pf_rd_p=cb099553-8b1e-4ecd-bf9d-2789a0a6379a&amp;pf_rd_r=K7TJP1VZEH6TREBBJYE8&amp;pd_rd_wg=waqNx&amp;pd_rd_r=477d2d6f-78f5-4e13-ab30-6fd7ade6287e&amp;th=1">购买连结</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/30/amazon-prime-day-tiktok-shop-promotion/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Amazon Prime Day 下月中举行   TikTok 一周前办促销活动抢饮头啖汤</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/amazon-prime-day-2024/shop_guide/">【专题】Amazon Prime Day 2024 消费攻略　抵买 SSD + Pixel 手机</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
